name: custom lego back to the future booster pack
description: this is what the lego set was missing .. you get the three hover boards martys biffs and the question mark board .. all hand cast resin in the color they are ment to be .. .. so you get 3 boards and a left and right leg cast in light blue to match your original marty lego figure

name: MAN ACTION  "ROTO" from rotary art by mad joe
description:
the first in the new line of MAN ACTION FIGURES by mad joe and overkill creations in collaboration with ROTARY ART CLOTHING and ACCESSORIES 

4.5 inches 5 points of articulation using my cleverly invented silicon band articulation system, its hand painted and cast resin we only  have 10 first run of figures . they come numbered and he comes on a re-usable laminated back card, so you can keep him in the package or play with him .  
his race suit is also GLOW IN THE DARK!!!

name: the boulder-man
description:
the first figure in the resin syndicate line
the boulder-man 
4 inches tall with 6 points of articulation
its a 25 piece limited run 
in 3 different colorways 
a 8 green, 9 orange and 8 black.
the design sculpt/bootleg and card art is by mad joe customizer 
of overkill creations
the card on the figure is laminated and reopenable so you can take the figure in and out of its packaging
